data.description: This beautiful 4BR/2BA/2CG Spring Hill home is located in the sought after Sterling Hill Subdivision in the Covey Run Gated Community.   The spacious OPEN CONCEPT design throughout the kitchen and great room make this home a perfect layout for entertaining family and friends.  The kitchen has a corner walk-in pantry and counter bar and comes with all appliances including refrigerator, dishwasher, electric range/oven with built-in microwave.  The primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet with laminate flooring, a private bathroom with dual sinks, and a walk-in shower. Two other bedrooms at the front of the house share a second bathroom.  A fourth bedroom is located off the foyer and can also serve as an office.  You'll find laminate flooring throughout the hallway and great room, with tile in the foyer, kitchen, laundry room and bathrooms.  The fully fenced backyard backs up to a wooded area and comes with a 4' decorative fence in the rear and 6' privacy fence on each side.  The Sterling Hill Subdivision boasts (2) resort style pools, (2) fitness centers, playground, doggie park and tennis/basketball courts to use at your leisure! Centrally located with access to major highways, schools, shopping, medical facilities, restaurants and golf courses.
